{
  "stem": "19982.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I said, well, they probably talk-- that's why I don't understand what they are talking because I'm in heaven.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was going in coma and out of coma.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, you don't-- and then again, I didn't know what happened till finally I got better.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then I found out that I was left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I found out later that my uncle was putting up a terrible fight [CRYING] not to leave me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[SOBBING] But they didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They just left me alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this I will never forget-- when I came completely to consciousness and I found myself there, all alone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I didn't understand the language.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I didn't know happened to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "This feeling-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] till I die [SOBBING] I will remember.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[CRYING] [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And then took-- I don't really remember the time because I don't know how long.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I got a little bit better, stronger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They-- there was no medicine there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There were no doctor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There was just a felcher.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "A felcher is like a doctor's associate, you know, like-- but no doctor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There were, like, to-- and people every single day were dying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They-- this was called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You know, people-- they brought there people with typhoid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Would they-- you die, finished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Every single day, few people died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they took them out from the room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then, when I was a little bit better and I got off the bed, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I saw there a, a woman.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I saw that somebody is coming to her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "A man is coming to her, but they didn't let him in-- but through the window.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And this woman was talking with the brother Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I didn't speak too well Jewish, but I spoke Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
